<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>識讲粤语 · 测一测你几劲</title>
  <meta name="description" content="3 分钟测出你的粤语等级 + MBTI 风格人格 + 学习时长 + 匹配课程和语伴">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/style.css?v=20260607b">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+SC:wght@400;700;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>
  <main class="container">
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="display" style="font-size: 18px; color: var(--lime); margin-bottom: 8px;">識讲粤语 · YUE 测</div>
      <h1 class="display">
        你嘅<span style="color: var(--yellow);">粤语</span>，<br>
        究竟去到边度？
      </h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">
        3 分钟 14 道题，测出你的<br>
        <strong>水平等级</strong> + <strong>MBTI 风格人格</strong> + <strong>学习时长</strong>
      </p>
      <a class="btn btn-primary btn-lg glow" href="test.html">测一测我几劲 🚀</a>
      <p class="text-sm muted mt-2">已有 12,000+ 学员测过 · 真实数据驱动</p>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <h2 class="display center">3 个等级，你是哪一个？</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-3 mt-3">
        <div class="card">
          <div class="level-badge level-entry">入门</div>
          <h3 class="display inline-icon">听唔明仔 <i data-icon="egg"></i></h3>
          <p class="text-sm muted mt-1">「你讲咩啊？」</p>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm">看到「你食咗饭未啊」要反应 3 秒。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <div class="level-badge level-mid">进阶</div>
          <h3 class="display inline-icon">識少少扮代表 <i data-icon="fox"></i></h3>
          <p class="text-sm muted mt-1">「咩嚟㗎？」</p>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm">能听懂日常对话，但开口卡壳。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <div class="level-badge level-high">高阶</div>
          <h3 class="display inline-icon">嘴替本替 <i data-icon="crown"></i></h3>
          <p class="text-sm muted mt-1">「我嚟讲嘢啦！」</p>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm">俚语/俗语/职场粤语满级。</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <h2 class="display center">测完你会拿到</h2>
      <div class="stack mt-3">
        <div class="card-flat row" style="gap:16px;">
          <i data-icon="target" style="font-size:36px; color: var(--blue);"></i>
          <div>
            <div class="bold">你的粤语等级</div>
            <div class="text-sm muted">听唔明仔 / 識少少 / 嘴替本替</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card-flat row" style="gap:16px;">
          <i data-icon="dna" style="font-size:36px; color: var(--blue);"></i>
          <div>
            <div class="bold">你的 MBTI 风格人格</div>
            <div class="text-sm muted">16 型之一 · 比如「SPWI 速成·听讲·独狼·学院派」</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card-flat row" style="gap:16px;">
          <i data-icon="clock" style="font-size:36px; color: var(--blue);"></i>
          <div>
            <div class="bold">你的学习时长</div>
            <div class="text-sm muted">按年龄/地域/每日时长算的精确预测</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card-flat row" style="gap:16px;">
          <i data-icon="handshake" style="font-size:36px; color: var(--blue);"></i>
          <div>
            <div class="bold">匹配语伴 + 课程</div>
            <div class="text-sm muted">按你等级筛的 3-5 位语伴 + 3 门主推课</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section center">
      <h2 class="display">免费 · 不用登录 · 1 分钟出结果</h2>
      <a class="btn btn-primary btn-lg mt-3" href="test.html">开始测试 <i data-icon="arrow-right"></i></a>
    </section>
  </main>

  <footer class="footer">
    識讲粤语 · 由 Vickey 老师主理 · 测试数据仅作学习建议参考
  </footer>

  <script src="js/common.js?v=20260607b"></script>
  <script>
    Cantonese.initTheme();
    Cantonese.injectThemeToggle();
    Cantonese.injectTopbar('home');
    Cantonese.initIcons();
    Cantonese.initScrollReveal();
  </script>
</body>
</html>
